title: Ebro In The Morning - Yankees Eliminated + In-Laws Meeting

itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 10/24/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio talking about the Yankees elimination, meeting the in-laws, Dahmer, and so much more! 

All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
